### Create property
POST http://localhost:3000/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Apartment Marbella 01",
  "address": "Marbella Center",
  "city": "Marbella",
  "bedrooms": 2,
  "bathrooms": 1,
  "maxGuests": 4,
  "wifiName": "StayFlow",
  "wifiPassword": "12345678",
  "doorCode": "2026"
}

### Create booking
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "propertyId": "PASTE_PROPERTY_ID",
  "guestName": "John Smith",
  "guestEmail": "john@example.com",
  "checkInDate": "2026-08-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-08-05",
  "amount": 850,
  "source": "Direct"
}

### Get tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### Complete task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/PASTE_TASK_ID/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "photos": ["kitchen.jpg", "bathroom.jpg", "bedroom.jpg"]
}

### Open guest link
GET http://localhost:3000/api/guest/PASTE_GUEST_LINK
